      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "narrative",
          "text": "And as he sat upon the mount of Olives, the disciples came unto him privately, saying,"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Tell us, when shall these things be? and what shall be the sign of thy coming, and of the end of the world?",
